{"tid":1718932,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[化學撚同我全部入黎 ] TG毒害全香港人 極需要證明呢一點","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T12:40:33.000Z","uid":122197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a26d28946099d44744a9de9318799de1c675a562","tid":1718932,"uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:25:46.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人聽到催淚彈呢個字眼，覺得都係流下眼水，但實情係，TG高溫燃燒下，釋出二噁英，已經有前線記者患上不治既氯痤瘡 （氯痤瘡是目前唯一可確認，人體積存高濃度二噁英的表徵。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%AF%E7%97%A4%E7%98%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%25AF%25E7%2597%25A4%25E7%2598%25A1%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=bb3101bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%25AF%25E7%2597%25A4%25E7%2598%25A1%2F&h=9ea8b36d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%AF%E7%97%A4%E7%98%A1/</a><br />\n<br />\n中大2000幾個催淚彈，已經同毒氣屠城無分別！！！！從藍絲親戚收到佢個狗朋友既消息，狗內部正準備嘗試證明TG成份無害。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無害佢老味，個TG未爆可以係無害，爆個下產生既高溫，就係二噁英既來源。唔可以俾狗咁樣耍手段欺騙市民。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我諗住搵一啲方法，用科學證明二噁英 （或其它有毒元素）既存在，用證據撚醒班廢老藍絲，唔好覺得躲係屋企就無事，要一齊屌狗唔俾佢地亂射TG<br />\n<br />\n之前屋企懷疑漏煤氣，買左個有機氣體檢測儀，理論上可以測埋TG，但由於並非針對二噁英做檢測，出左數據都唔夠說服力。大家有無其他計？"},{"pid":"9704cc6b35c70d4c37aee28cefd6a8db249708d9","tid":1718932,"uid":327414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"dioxins 係致癌<br />\n政府化驗所每日都有做食物裏dioxins 含量"},{"pid":"670f3faafa7ec423c09bf5435ec8c3bf6e5e6240","tid":1718932,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:06:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8c00b58915bbda163ea60488f71c4b67e263128","tid":1718932,"uid":299779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"借個靚位po張長輩圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWeWou1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWeWou1.png&h=8701f13d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06c11ae23d7dbc8530047eb775d4b433775c1d0d","tid":1718932,"uid":5208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"通常聽係用GC MS/MS做"},{"pid":"f67aa397019449963507a00bab76b6c362b91597","tid":1718932,"uid":5208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"除非揾到專業人做，如果唔係好難有公信力，除左dioxin重有好多殘餘既chemical結晶orz微塵粒都應該有生物毒性，cytotoxicity test可能都要考慮，但一般應該有規定人體可承受標準，作用唔大，早排有隊chem engineer做左相關test，可以再睇睇佢地既詳細報告？但暫時未揾到佢地release既檢測數據，我再揾下有無先"},{"pid":"f4ad8e96a795ac56baf74fe2ba0a59c9e904044b","tid":1718932,"uid":143474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:42:30.000Z","msg":"有冇收集空氣樣本<br />\n再送去大學實驗室化驗<br />\n<br />\nhk chem phd/mphil student 唔該做野<br />\n學校啲gcms 任你用"},{"pid":"e43b2408486b8b10038ab4250f5ff8292a7f9af8","tid":1718932,"uid":122197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"我都好想有辦法聯絡浸大二噁英化驗lab。個lab都算出名：<a href=\"http://vitality.hk/page.aspx?page=hknews20090924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvitality.hk%2Fpage.aspx%3Fpage%3Dhknews20090924&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=9bbca684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vitality.hk/page.aspx?page=hknews20090924</a>"}]}